PHASE 0: SETUP + BASICS OF RUNNING JAVA (1-2 DAYS)
[ ] INSTALL JDK
[ ] SET PATH / JAVA_HOME
[ ] IDE: INTELLIJ / ECLIPSE / VS CODE
[ ] HOW JAVA RUNS: .JAVA -> JAVAC -> .CLASS -> JVM
[ ] COMMAND LINE RUN (OPTIONAL BUT GOOD)

PHASE 1: CORE BASICS (FOUNDATION) (1-2 WEEKS)


SYNTAX + PROGRAM STRUCTURE
[ ] CLASS, MAIN METHOD, PRINTING
[ ] COMMENTS, FORMAT, NAMING RULES


VARIABLES + DATA TYPES
[ ] PRIMITIVES: BYTE SHORT INT LONG FLOAT DOUBLE CHAR BOOLEAN
[ ] LITERALS, TYPE CASTING (WIDENING / NARROWING)
[ ] FINAL (CONSTANTS), DEFAULT VALUES (CLASS LEVEL)


OPERATORS
[ ] ARITHMETIC, RELATIONAL, LOGICAL
[ ] INCREMENT/DECREMENT, ASSIGNMENT
[ ] BITWISE BASICS, PRECEDENCE


CONTROL FLOW
[ ] IF / ELSE, SWITCH
[ ] LOOPS: FOR, WHILE, DO-WHILE
[ ] BREAK, CONTINUE


METHODS (FUNCTIONS)
[ ] PARAMETERS, RETURN TYPES
[ ] METHOD OVERLOADING
[ ] RECURSION BASICS



PHASE 2: ARRAYS + STRINGS + BASIC PROBLEM SOLVING (2-3 WEEKS)
ARRAYS
[ ] 1D ARRAYS: CREATE, ACCESS, TRAVERSE
[ ] 2D ARRAYS: ROW/COL, MATRIX BASICS
[ ] COMMON PROBLEMS: MAX/MIN, SUM, REVERSE, ROTATE, SEARCH
STRINGS
[ ] STRING VS STRINGBUILDER VS STRINGBUFFER
[ ] IMPORTANT METHODS: LENGTH, CHARAT, SUBSTRING, INDEXOF, SPLIT
[ ] PROBLEMS: PALINDROME, ANAGRAM, FREQUENCY, REMOVE DUPLICATES
BASIC ALGORITHMS
[ ] LINEAR SEARCH, BINARY SEARCH
[ ] SORTING: BUBBLE, SELECTION, INSERTION

